                  <td align=left valign=top><div align=justify><font face='Arial,Sans-Serif' size='-1'><b>Happy New Year!</b> Created pages for four Necronomicon Press publications: <a href="/study/bios/aav.aspx"><i>Ave atque Vale: Reminiscences of H. P. Lovecraft</i></a> (edited by S. T. Joshi &amp; David E. Schultz), <a href="/writings/sources/arsa.aspx"><i>A Facsimile Reproduction of</i> The Annual Report on the Science of Astronomy, <i>1904</i></a> (afterword by S. T. Joshi), <a href="/writings/sources/hwr.aspx"><i>Herbert West&mdash;Reanimator</i></a> (illustrated by Robert H. Knox), and <a href="/writings/sources/cs.aspx"><i>The Colour Out of Space</i></a> (illustrated by Jason C. Eckhardt).</font></div></td>
               </tr>
               
               <tr>
                  <td align=right valign=top nowrap><font face='Arial,Sans-Serif' size='-1'>15 December 2018:&nbsp;</td>
